        <div class="section">
            <h2>My Background</h2>
            <p>My name is Harshit Sharma, and I am a student pursuing B.Tech in Computer Science and Engineering. Coming from a family where my father works as a taxi driver, funding my education posed a significant challenge. However, I was determined to pursue my Bachelor's degree, even if it meant facing rejection from banks due to my father's poor credit score.</p>
