        <div class="section">
            <h2>Challenges Faced</h2>
            <p>I spent countless hours at various banks, facing disappointment and frustration as many rejected my loan applications. Despite the hurdles, I managed to secure admission to college. It was a new world for me, as I encountered English books and teachers for the first time, coming from a Hindi medium background.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Overcoming Obstacles</h2>
            <p>The uncertainty of how long I could afford to stay in college loomed over me. However, I continued to believe in divine intervention and persisted in applying for loans. After three years of relentless efforts, I received support from several foundations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Dreamers Platform</h2>
            <p>This experience inspired me to ensure that no student faces similar challenges in pursuing their education. Thus, I founded Dreamers, a platform where students can find comprehensive information about education loans, including application procedures and available assistance from various foundations and donors.</p>
        </div>
